			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump, swim, hold to jump higher:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X or Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire Mega Power, fire Mega Buster, press and hold to charge:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire Mega Buster, press and hold to charge blast, cancel item in menu:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change Mega Power, switch menu in Mega Power screen:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Slide under narrow passages:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle or X Button + D-Pad down</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open reset menu from Mega Power screen:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open Mega Power screen, select item in menu:
